### 7. Contributing Documentation

**Absolute Path:** `/private/var/folders/vq/9q38rw0x2455zr_whqcrjbhr0000gn/T/planmode-bench-wt-run-1775496928255-ftqim4/contributing/add-new-provider.md`

**Process for adding a new provider:**

1. Create new folder `packages/<provider>`
2. Set version in `packages/<provider>/package.json` to `0.0.0`
3. Create changeset for new package with `major`
4. Add examples to `examples/ai-functions/src/*/<provider>.ts` (depending on model types)
5. Add documentation in `content/providers/01-ai-sdk-providers/<last number + 10>-<provider>.mdx`

**Reference PR:** https://github.com/vercel/ai/pull/8136/files

**Pre-release considerations:** If main is in beta release mode, no further action needed (avoid backporting to stable branch to prevent npm version conflicts).

